<sect1>
    <title>Supported OS</title>
    <para>
        NOC was created to work at almost any UNIX-style systems.
        NOC is reported to be supported on:
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>MacOS X</listitem>
            <listitem>Solaris 10</listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </para>
</sect1>
    
